sentences: John Molo (born 1953, Bethesda, Maryland) is an American rock and jazz drummer and percussionist.
Early Years =
Molo was the drummer for Bruce Hornsby and the Range when the band won the Grammy Award for Best New Artist of 1986.
After the Range disbanded in 1990, Molo continued to collaborate and tour with Hornsby until 2000.

In May 2009, Molo joined the band Moonalice.
